node.text: I’m so happy and grateful to announce that our company just made the @incmagazine list of fastest growing companies in America! We did this by helping so many people transform their lives and their businesses. So if you’ve ever wanted to play with a winning team- I’d like to invite you now. DM me if you’re ready to work on your business credit or your personal credit. I also want to invite you to reach out to me if you could use an extra revenue stream- i’m now looking for affiliates who’d be interested in making a dollar and a difference at the same time! We’ve only got 4 months left in the year- let’s get it!! #DM me with the words #BusinessCredit #PersonalCredit or #makemoneywithhoney

node.text: Did you guys know that there are 4 different communication types that can be categorized as seasons? Summer personalities are the life of the party and tend to be laid back. Spring personalities are very drawn to helping others and fighting for a cause. Winter personalities tend to be very strong willed, unbending, alpha types. Fall personalities are highly analytical, detail oriented and stoic. #novaemoney #inc5000
